sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant URL as Router
    participant VIEW as Expense / Reporting ViewSet
    participant MIXIN as Org Scoped Mixin
    participant SER as Serializer
    participant SVC as Service Layer
    participant SEL as Selector Layer
    participant DB as Database

    Note over FE,DB: Write Flow
    FE->>URL: POST /api/v1/expenses/
    URL->>VIEW: route request
    VIEW->>MIXIN: resolve request.organization
    VIEW->>SER: validate write payload
    SER->>SVC: build payload + call service
    SVC->>DB: create/update/archive expense
    VIEW-->>FE: serialized expense response

    Note over FE,DB: Read Flow
    FE->>URL: GET /api/v1/expenses/
    URL->>VIEW: route request
    VIEW->>MIXIN: resolve org + filters
    VIEW->>SEL: list_expenses(...)
    SEL->>DB: query org-scoped expenses
    DB-->>SEL: result rows
    VIEW->>SER: shape read contract
    VIEW-->>FE: list/detail response

    Note over FE,DB: Reporting Flow
    FE->>URL: GET /api/v1/expense-reporting/dashboard/
    URL->>VIEW: route request
    VIEW->>MIXIN: resolve org + reporting filters
    VIEW->>SEL: compute monthly/category/building aggregates
    SEL->>DB: grouped aggregate query
    DB-->>SEL: grouped totals
    VIEW->>SVC: assemble dashboard payload
    VIEW->>SER: shape chart contracts
    VIEW-->>FE: reporting JSON
